{"thig16.1:0.1":"Therigatha 16.1 ","thig16.1:0.2":"Mahanipata ","thig16.1:0.3":"Sumedhatherigatha ","thig16.1:1.1":"Mantavatiya nagare, ","thig16.1:1.2":"Ranno koncassa aggamahesiya; ","thig16.1:1.3":"Dhita asim sumedha, ","thig16.1:1.4":"Pasadita sasanakarehi. ","thig16.1:2.1":"Silavati cittakatha, ","thig16.1:2.2":"Bahussuta buddhasasane vinita; ","thig16.1:2.3":"Matapitaro upagamma, ","thig16.1:2.4":"Bhanati “ubhayo nisametha. ","thig16.1:3.1":"Nibbanabhirataham, ","thig16.1:3.2":"Asassatam bhavagatam yadipi dibbam; ","thig16.1:3.3":"Kimangam pana tuccha kama, ","thig16.1:3.4":"Appassada bahuvighata. ","thig16.1:4.1":"Kama katuka asi, ","thig16.1:4.2":"Visupama yesu mucchita bala; ","thig16.1:4.3":"Te digharattam niraye, ","thig16.1:4.4":"Samappita hannante dukkhita. ","thig16.1:5.1":"Socanti papakamma, ","thig16.1:5.2":"Vinipate papavaddhino sada; ","thig16.1:5.3":"Kayena ca vacaya ca, ","thig16.1:5.4":"Manasa ca asamvuta bala. ","thig16.1:6.1":"Bala te duppanna, ","thig16.1:6.2":"Acetana dukkhasamudayoruddha; ","thig16.1:6.3":"Desente ajananta, ","thig16.1:6.4":"Na bujjhare ariyasaccani. ","thig16.1:7.1":"Saccani amma buddhavaradesitani, ","thig16.1:7.2":"Te bahutara ajananta ye; ","thig16.1:7.3":"Abhinandanti bhavagatam, ","thig16.1:7.4":"Pihenti devesu upapattim. ","thig16.1:8.1":"Devesupi upapatti, ","thig16.1:8.2":"Asassata bhavagate aniccamhi; ","thig16.1:8.3":"Na ca santasanti bala, ","thig16.1:8.4":"Punappunam jayitabbassa. ","thig16.1:9.1":"Cattaro vinipata, ","thig16.1:9.2":"Duve ca gatiyo kathanci labbhanti; ","thig16.1:9.3":"Na ca vinipatagatanam, ","thig16.1:9.4":"Pabbajja atthi nirayesu. ","thig16.1:10.1":"Anujanatha mam ubhayo, ","thig16.1:10.2":"Pabbajitum dasabalassa pavacane; ","thig16.1:10.3":"Appossukka ghatissam, ","thig16.1:10.4":"Jatimaranappahanaya. ","thig16.1:11.1":"Kim bhavagate abhinanditena, ","thig16.1:11.2":"Kayakalina asarena; ","thig16.1:11.3":"Bhavatanhaya nirodha, ","thig16.1:11.4":"Anujanatha pabbajissami. ","thig16.1:12.1":"Buddhanam uppado vivajjito, ","thig16.1:12.2":"Akkhano khano laddho; ","thig16.1:12.3":"Silani brahmacariyam, ","thig16.1:12.4":"Yavajivam na duseyyam”. ","thig16.1:13.1":"Evam bhanati sumedha, ","thig16.1:13.2":"Matapitaro “na tava aharam; ","thig16.1:13.3":"Aharissam gahattha, ","thig16.1:13.4":"Maranavasam gatava hessami”. ","thig16.1:14.1":"Mata dukkhita rodati pita ca, ","thig16.1:14.2":"Assa sabbaso samabhihato; ","thig16.1:14.3":"Ghatenti sannapetum, ","thig16.1:14.4":"Pasadatale chamapatitam. ","thig16.1:15.1":"“Utthehi puttaka kim soci, ","thig16.1:15.2":"Tena dinnasi varanavatimhi; ","thig16.1:15.3":"Raja anikaratto, ","thig16.1:15.4":"Abhirupo tassa tvam dinna. ","thig16.1:16.1":"Aggamahesi bhavissasi, ","thig16.1:16.2":"Anikarattassa rajino bhariya; ","thig16.1:16.3":"Silani brahmacariyam, ","thig16.1:16.4":"Pabbajja dukkara puttaka. ","thig16.1:17.1":"Rajje ana dhanamissariyam, ","thig16.1:17.2":"Bhoga sukha daharikasi; ","thig16.1:17.3":"Bhunjahi kamabhoge, ","thig16.1:17.4":"Vareyyam hotu te putta”. ","thig16.1:18.1":"Atha ne bhanati sumedha, ","thig16.1:18.2":"“Ma edisikani bhavagatamasaram; ","thig16.1:18.3":"Pabbajja va hohiti, ","thig16.1:18.4":"Maranam va me na ceva vareyyam. ","thig16.1:19.1":"Kimiva putikayamasucim, ","thig16.1:19.2":"Savanagandham bhayanakam kunapam; ","thig16.1:19.3":"Abhisamviseyyam bhastam, ","thig16.1:19.4":"Asakim paggharitam asucipunnam. ","thig16.1:20.1":"Kimiva taham jananti, ","thig16.1:20.2":"Vikulakam mamsasonitupalittam; ","thig16.1:20.3":"Kimikulalayam sakunabhattam, ","thig16.1:20.4":"Kalevaram kissa diyyati. ","thig16.1:21.1":"Nibbuyhati susanam, ","thig16.1:21.2":"Aciram kayo apetavinnano; ","thig16.1:21.3":"Chuddho kalingaram viya, ","thig16.1:21.4":"Jigucchamanehi natihi. ","thig16.1:22.1":"Chuddhuna nam susane, ","thig16.1:22.2":"Parabhattam nhayanti jigucchanta; ","thig16.1:22.3":"Niyaka matapitaro, ","thig16.1:22.4":"Kim pana sadharana janata. ","thig16.1:23.1":"Ajjhosita asare, ","thig16.1:23.2":"Kalevare atthinharusanghate; ","thig16.1:23.3":"Khelassuccarassava, ","thig16.1:23.4":"Paripunne putikayamhi. ","thig16.1:24.1":"Yo nam vinibbhujitva, ","thig16.1:24.2":"Abbhantaramassa bahiram kayira; ","thig16.1:24.3":"Gandhassa asahamana, ","thig16.1:24.4":"Sakapi mata jiguccheyya. ","thig16.1:25.1":"Khandhadhatuayatanam, ","thig16.1:25.2":"Sankhatam jatimulakam dukkham; ","thig16.1:25.3":"Yoniso anuvicinanti, ","thig16.1:25.4":"Vareyyam kissa iccheyyam. ","thig16.1:26.1":"Divase divase tisatti, ","thig16.1:26.2":"Satani navanava pateyyum kayamhi; ","thig16.1:26.3":"Vassasatampi ca ghato, ","thig16.1:26.4":"Seyyo dukkhassa cevam khayo. ","thig16.1:27.1":"Ajjhupagacche ghatam, ","thig16.1:27.2":"Yo vinnayevam satthuno vacanam; ","thig16.1:27.3":"‘Digho tesam samsaro, ","thig16.1:27.4":"Punappunam hannamananam’. ","thig16.1:28.1":"Devesu manussesu ca, ","thig16.1:28.2":"Tiracchanayoniya asurakaye; ","thig16.1:28.3":"Petesu ca nirayesu ca, ","thig16.1:28.4":"Aparimita dissare ghata. ","thig16.1:29.1":"Ghata nirayesu bahu, ","thig16.1:29.2":"Vinipatagatassa piliyamanassa; ","thig16.1:29.3":"Devesupi attanam, ","thig16.1:29.4":"Nibbanasukha param natthi. ","thig16.1:30.1":"Patta te nibbanam, ","thig16.1:30.2":"Ye yutta dasabalassa pavacane; ","thig16.1:30.3":"Appossukka ghatenti, ","thig16.1:30.4":"Jatimaranappahanaya. ","thig16.1:31.1":"Ajjeva tatabhinikkha- ","thig16.1:31.2":"Missam bhogehi kim asarehi; ","thig16.1:31.3":"Nibbinna me kama, ","thig16.1:31.4":"Vantasama talavatthukata”. ","thig16.1:32.1":"Sa cevam bhanati pitara- ","thig16.1:32.2":"Manikaratto ca yassa sa dinna; ","thig16.1:32.3":"Upayasi varanavate, ","thig16.1:32.4":"Vareyyamupatthite kale. ","thig16.1:33.1":"Atha asitanicitamuduke, ","thig16.1:33.2":"Kese khaggena chindiya sumedha; ","thig16.1:33.3":"Pasadam pidahitva, ","thig16.1:33.4":"Pathamajjhanam samapajji. ","thig16.1:34.1":"Sa ca tahim samapanna, ","thig16.1:34.2":"Anikaratto ca agato nagaram; ","thig16.1:34.3":"Pasade ca sumedha, ","thig16.1:34.4":"Aniccasannam subhaveti. ","thig16.1:35.1":"Sa ca manasi karoti, ","thig16.1:35.2":"Anikaratto ca aruhi turitam; ","thig16.1:35.3":"Manikanakabhusitango, ","thig16.1:35.4":"Katanjali yacati sumedham. ","thig16.1:36.1":"“Rajje anadhanamissa- ","thig16.1:36.2":"Riyam bhoga sukha daharikasi; ","thig16.1:36.3":"Bhunjahi kamabhoge, ","thig16.1:36.4":"Kamasukha dullabha loke. ","thig16.1:37.1":"Nissattham te rajjam, ","thig16.1:37.2":"Bhoge bhunjassu dehi danani; ","thig16.1:37.3":"Ma dummana ahosi, ","thig16.1:37.4":"Matapitaro te dukkhita”. ","thig16.1:38.1":"Tam tam bhanati sumedha, ","thig16.1:38.2":"Kamehi anatthika vigatamoha; ","thig16.1:38.3":"“Ma kame abhinandi, ","thig16.1:38.4":"Kamesvadinavam passa. ","thig16.1:39.1":"Catuddipo raja, ","thig16.1:39.2":"Mandhata asi kamabhoginamaggo; ","thig16.1:39.3":"Atitto kalankato, ","thig16.1:39.4":"Na cassa paripurita iccha. ","thig16.1:40.1":"Satta ratanani vasseyya, ","thig16.1:40.2":"Vutthima dasadisa samantena; ","thig16.1:40.3":"Na catthi titti kamanam, ","thig16.1:40.4":"Atittava maranti nara. ","thig16.1:41.1":"Asisunupama kama, ","thig16.1:41.2":"kama sappasiropama; ","thig16.1:41.3":"Ukkopama anudahanti, ","thig16.1:41.4":"atthikankala sannibha. ","thig16.1:42.1":"Anicca adhuva kama, ","thig16.1:42.2":"bahudukkha mahavisa; ","thig16.1:42.3":"Ayogulova santatto, ","thig16.1:42.4":"aghamula dukhapphala. ","thig16.1:43.1":"Rukkhapphalupama kama, ","thig16.1:43.2":"mamsapesupama dukha; ","thig16.1:43.3":"Supinopama vancaniya, ","thig16.1:43.4":"kama yacitakupama. ","thig16.1:44.1":"Sattisulupama kama, ","thig16.1:44.2":"rogo gando agham nigham; ","thig16.1:44.3":"Angarakasusadisa, ","thig16.1:44.4":"aghamulam bhayam vadho. ","thig16.1:45.1":"Evam bahudukkha kama, ","thig16.1:45.2":"akkhata antarayika; ","thig16.1:45.3":"Gacchatha na me bhavagate, ","thig16.1:45.4":"vissaso atthi attano. ","thig16.1:46.1":"Kim mama paro karissati, ","thig16.1:46.2":"Attano sisamhi dayhamanamhi; ","thig16.1:46.3":"Anubandhe jaramarane, ","thig16.1:46.4":"Tassa ghataya ghatitabbam”. ","thig16.1:47.1":"Dvaram apapuritvanaham, ","thig16.1:47.2":"Matapitaro anikarattanca; ","thig16.1:47.3":"Disvana chamam nisinne, ","thig16.1:47.4":"Rodante idamavocam. ","thig16.1:48.1":"“Digho balanam samsaro, ","thig16.1:48.2":"Punappunanca rodatam; ","thig16.1:48.3":"Anamatagge pitu marane, ","thig16.1:48.4":"Bhatu vadhe attano ca vadhe. ","thig16.1:49.1":"Assu thannam rudhiram, ","thig16.1:49.2":"Samsaram anamataggato saratha; ","thig16.1:49.3":"Sattanam samsaratam, ","thig16.1:49.4":"Sarahi atthinanca sannicayam. ","thig16.1:50.1":"Sara caturodadhi, ","thig16.1:50.2":"Upanite assuthannarudhiramhi; ","thig16.1:50.3":"Sara ekakappamatthinam, ","thig16.1:50.4":"Sancayam vipulena samam. ","thig16.1:51.1":"Anamatagge samsarato, ","thig16.1:51.2":"Mahim jambudipamupanitam; ","thig16.1:51.3":"Kolatthimattagulika, ","thig16.1:51.4":"Mata matusveva nappahonti. ","thig16.1:52.1":"Tinakatthasakhapalasam, ","thig16.1:52.2":"Upanitam anamataggato sara; ","thig16.1:52.3":"Caturangulika ghatika, ","thig16.1:52.4":"Pitupitusveva nappahonti. ","thig16.1:53.1":"Sara kanakacchapam pubba- ","thig16.1:53.2":"Samudde aparato ca yugachiddam; ","thig16.1:53.3":"Siram tassa ca patimukkam, ","thig16.1:53.4":"Manussalabhamhi opammam. ","thig16.1:54.1":"Sara rupam phenapindopa- ","thig16.1:54.2":"Massa kayakalino asarassa; ","thig16.1:54.3":"Khandhe passa anicce, ","thig16.1:54.4":"Sarahi niraye bahuvighate. ","thig16.1:55.1":"Sara katasim vaddhente, ","thig16.1:55.2":"Punappunam tasu tasu jatisu; ","thig16.1:55.3":"Sara kumbhilabhayani ca, ","thig16.1:55.4":"Sarahi cattari saccani. ","thig16.1:56.1":"Amatamhi vijjamane, ","thig16.1:56.2":"Kim tava pancakatukena pitena; ","thig16.1:56.3":"Sabba hi kamaratiyo, ","thig16.1:56.4":"Katukatara pancakatukena. ","thig16.1:57.1":"Amatamhi vijjamane, ","thig16.1:57.2":"Kim tava kamehi ye parilaha; ","thig16.1:57.3":"Sabba hi kamaratiyo, ","thig16.1:57.4":"Jalita kuthita kampita santapita. ","thig16.1:58.1":"Asapattamhi samane, ","thig16.1:58.2":"Kim tava kamehi ye bahusapatta; ","thig16.1:58.3":"Rajaggicoraudakappiyehi, ","thig16.1:58.4":"Sadharana kama bahusapatta. ","thig16.1:59.1":"Mokkhamhi vijjamane, ","thig16.1:59.2":"Kim tava kamehi yesu vadhabandho; ","thig16.1:59.3":"Kamesu hi asakama, ","thig16.1:59.4":"Vadhabandhadukhani anubhonti. ","thig16.1:60.1":"Adipita tinukka, ","thig16.1:60.2":"Ganhantam dahanti neva muncantam; ","thig16.1:60.3":"Ukkopama hi kama, ","thig16.1:60.4":"Dahanti ye te na muncanti. ","thig16.1:61.1":"Ma appakassa hetu, ","thig16.1:61.2":"Kamasukhassa vipulam jahi sukham; ","thig16.1:61.3":"Ma puthulomova balisam, ","thig16.1:61.4":"Gilitva paccha vihannasi. ","thig16.1:62.1":"Kamam kamesu damassu, ","thig16.1:62.2":"Tava sunakhova sankhalabaddho; ","thig16.1:62.3":"Kahinti khu tam kama, ","thig16.1:62.4":"Chata sunakhamva candala. ","thig16.1:63.1":"Aparimitanca dukkham, ","thig16.1:63.2":"Bahuni ca cittadomanassani; ","thig16.1:63.3":"Anubhohisi kamayutto, ","thig16.1:63.4":"Patinissaja addhuve kame. ","thig16.1:64.1":"Ajaramhi vijjamane, ","thig16.1:64.2":"Kim tava kamehi yesu jara; ","thig16.1:64.3":"Maranabyadhigahita, ","thig16.1:64.4":"Sabba sabbattha jatiyo. ","thig16.1:65.1":"Idamajaramidamamaram, ","thig16.1:65.2":"Idamajaramaram padamasokam; ","thig16.1:65.3":"Asapattamasambadham, ","thig16.1:65.4":"Akhalitamabhayam nirupatapam. ","thig16.1:66.1":"Adhigatamidam bahuhi, ","thig16.1:66.2":"Amatam ajjapi ca labhaniyamidam; ","thig16.1:66.3":"Yo yoniso payunjati, ","thig16.1:66.4":"Na ca sakka aghatamanena”. ","thig16.1:67.1":"Evam bhanati sumedha, ","thig16.1:67.2":"Sankharagate ratim alabhamana; ","thig16.1:67.3":"Anunenti anikarattam, ","thig16.1:67.4":"Kese ca chamam khipi sumedha. ","thig16.1:68.1":"Utthaya anikaratto, ","thig16.1:68.2":"Panjaliko yacatassa pitaram so; ","thig16.1:68.3":"“Vissajjetha sumedham, ","thig16.1:68.4":"Pabbajitum vimokkhasaccadassa”. ","thig16.1:69.1":"Vissajjita matapituhi, ","thig16.1:69.2":"pabbaji sokabhayabhita; ","thig16.1:69.3":"Cha abhinna sacchikata, ","thig16.1:69.4":"aggaphalam sikkhamanaya. ","thig16.1:70.1":"Acchariyamabbhutam tam, ","thig16.1:70.2":"Nibbanam asi rajakannaya; ","thig16.1:70.3":"Pubbenivasacaritam, ","thig16.1:70.4":"Yatha byakari pacchime kale. ","thig16.1:71.1":"“Bhagavati konagamane, ","thig16.1:71.2":"Sangharamamhi navanivesamhi; ","thig16.1:71.3":"Sakhiyo tisso janiyo, ","thig16.1:71.4":"Viharadanam adasimha. ","thig16.1:72.1":"Dasakkhattum satakkhattum, ","thig16.1:72.2":"Dasasatakkhattum satani ca satakkhattum; ","thig16.1:72.3":"Devesu uppajjimha, ","thig16.1:72.4":"Ko pana vado manussesu. ","thig16.1:73.1":"Devesu mahiddhika ahumha, ","thig16.1:73.2":"Manusakamhi ko pana vado; ","thig16.1:73.3":"Sattaratanassa mahesi, ","thig16.1:73.4":"Itthiratanam aham asim. ","thig16.1:74.1":"So hetu so pabhavo, ","thig16.1:74.2":"Tam mulam sava sasane khanti; ","thig16.1:74.3":"Tam pathamasamodhanam, ","thig16.1:74.4":"Tam dhammarataya nibbanam. ","thig16.1:75.1":"Evam karonti ye sadda- ","thig16.1:75.2":"Hanti vacanam anomapannassa; ","thig16.1:75.3":"Nibbindanti bhavagate, ","thig16.1:75.4":"Nibbinditva virajjanti”ti. ","thig16.1:76.1":"Ittham sudam sumedha theri gathayo abhasitthati. ","thig16.1:76.2":"Mahanipato nitthito. ","thig16.1:77.0":"Samatta therigathayo ","thig16.1:77.1":"Gathasatani cattari, ","thig16.1:77.2":"asiti puna cuddasa; ","thig16.1:77.3":"Theriyekuttarasata, ","thig16.1:77.4":"sabba ta asavakkhayati. ","thig16.1:77.5":"Therigathapali nitthita. "}